{"tid":245102,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"深市快報：傳樂視旗下酷派終聘300名應屆生 (10:16)","createTime":"2017-05-16T03:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T17:48:32.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5980d4888b0d1752ab0ad9a723a0c90e0d568d55","tid":245102,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/113527_2bcdc01cd61bed857576abea224fe297.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F113527_2bcdc01cd61bed857576abea224fe297.jpg&h=3c605eb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2UbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=3050a3e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】內媒報道，樂視(300104.SZ)旗下酷派集團(02369)日前將之前在內地招聘所得逾300名應屆畢業生全部解約，而酷派將進行賠償，分別為本科生3,000元人民幣(下同)，研究生4,000元，並承諾盡力幫忙轉介。<br />\n<br />\n酷派上月於香港交易所公布，截至2017年3月31日經營虧損約4.6億港元，預計2017年上半年的經營虧損會擴大到6億至8億元，相比2016年同期經營虧損1.628億元，將出現較大經營業績下滑。<br />\n<br />\n公司解釋，主因市場競爭激烈，而規劃中具有競爭力的新產品尚未上市，導致銷售收入規模下滑，預計2017年上半年較去年同期營業收入下滑逾50%；同時集團持續投入研發及市場銷售推廣活動，致2017年上半年費用支出未有改善。<br />\n<br />\n樂視及酷派集團目前一併停牌中，其中酷派自本年3月31日起停牌，以待刊發2016年度業績及有關任何重大審核結果的建議跟進工作安排。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170516/20170516101657fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170516%2F20170516101657fi.html&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2UbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=cf21339a\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170516/20170516101657fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"79ed46767c44d3c2e9cb5e0c968c7d3751958d9d","tid":245102,"uid":40179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T08:14:18.000Z","msg":"有冇糧出呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"802968a1bd1ee7be46de34547361feab4387cfb2","tid":245102,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:15:18.000Z","msg":"「終聘」？<br />\n<br />\n終乜撚野聘呀, 支那蝗語"},{"pid":"50289884048aefae3fe42daa593bc5533643bd0c","tid":245102,"uid":24310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:17:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「終聘」？<br />\n<br />\n終乜撚野聘呀, 支那蝗語</blockquote><br />\n以為最終聘用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98111c33327e915ed482773c5df04e1f2089d8f","tid":245102,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T16:20:30.000Z","msg":"而家啲傳媒已經唔識中文<br />\n解僱都唔識用"},{"pid":"b92646402af488bd2dc421ef851cce973c695098","tid":245102,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T17:47:50.000Z","msg":"終你老母臭系聘<br />\n<br />\n終止聘用？<br />\n終身聘用？<br />\n終於聘用？<br />\n<br />\n支那狗等收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811ff8d87e0ba805916a73337c2d564de97067d0","tid":245102,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T17:48:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>「終聘」？<br />\n<br />\n終乜撚野聘呀, 支那蝗語</blockquote><br />\n以為最終聘用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nX2"}]}